'''Low cost ophthalmoscope'''

==Problem==
A lack of low cost ophthalmoscopes in developing countries needed for training purposes.

==Summary==
a simple, effective, and
inexpensive training ophthalmoscope made with easily available material and
tools from art and office equipment shops. 

